<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #C9A96E;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 5px 0 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 20px;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            background-color: #C9A96E;
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #b8976a;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 12px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .price {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #C9A96E;
        }
        .highlight {
            background-color: #FFF8EE;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            border-left: 4px solid #D8A35D;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #F9F5F0;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #E8DFD3;
            margin: 16px 0;
        }
        .muted {
            color: #7A5C47;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            {% block header %}
                <h1>Khamareo</h1>
            {% endblock %}
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            {% block content %}{% endblock %}
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            {% block footer %}
                <p><strong>Merci de votre confiance !</strong></p>
                <p>L'équipe Khamareo</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 15px;">
                    <small>
                        Cet email a été envoyé automatiquement, merci de ne pas y répondre.<br>
                        Pour toute question, contactez-nous à <a href="mailto:support@khamareo.com">support@khamareo.com</a>
                    </small>
                </p>
            {% endblock %}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>